(defconst datetime-format--fmt-atom
  '(local . "%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S%:z")
  "ATOM date construct format (local time).

RFC4287: The Atom Syndication Format \"3.3.  Date Constructs\"
URL `https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc4287'")

